01:08:00.000 --> 01:08:02.000
documentation on the bigger decisions,

01:08:02.000 --> 01:08:04.000
why we're going one

01:08:04.000 --> 01:08:06.000
direction with an implementation

01:08:06.000 --> 01:08:08.000
