parity. You can do certain

01:11:32.000 --> 01:11:34.000
things in Python, you can't do in R.

01:11:34.000 --> 01:11:36.000
There are certain things in R you can't do

01:11:36.000 --> 01:11:38.000
in Python.

01:11:38.000 --> 01:11:40.000
Coming sort of from the background

01:11:40.000 --> 01:11:42.000
of more

01:11:42.000 --> 01:11:44.000
of a computer science approach to modeling

01:11:44.000 --> 01:11:46.000
and more of a statistic approach to modeling.

01:11:46.000 --> 01:11:48.000
Like something that is

01:11:48.000 --> 01:11:50.000
bread and butter, just statisticians being able

01:11:50.000 --> 01:11:52.000
to specify interactions

01:11:52.000 --> 01:11:54.000
in Python, whereas

01:11:54.000 --> 01:11:56.000
other things like

01:11:56.000 --> 01:11:58.000
